name: Symbols of the Witch - Rotating Pentagram - Back In Black
description:
Collection: Symbols of the Witch
Title: Rotating Pentagram
Version: Back In Black

A blessing of magic associated with strength, power, and sexual prowess. The black pentagram lends an air of elegance, sophistication, and authority. They who wield the sacred black pentagram in ritual guides the souls in the coven through the shadows of mystery and the unknown.
